metadata.name: A.I Piano Hit #1
metadata.description:
A piece of unique piano music NFT. Generated by artificial intelligence and machine learning. The algorithm will use machine learning to make the piano track enjoyable to humans. No two songs will be the same.

Visual artwork is a generative art generated by digital design and A.I tools.

MP3 file and MP4 will be sent to the NFT owner.

A unique masterpiece, and part of TheNFTco roadmap!
